### 1. Healthcheck (स्थिति जांचें)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/health

###

### 2. Get Categories Catalog (कैटेगरी लिस्ट मंगाएं)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/categories

###

### 3. Send OTP (OTP भेजें)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

###

### 4. Verify OTP (OTP वेरीफाई करके JWT टोकन पाएं)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "code": "123456",
  "role": "user"
}

###

### 5. Complete Profile (कस्टमर प्रोफाइल पूरी करें)
# नोट: नीचे "Bearer" के बाद स्टेप 4 से मिला टोकन पेस्ट करें
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/profile/complete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Rajesh Singh",
  "email": "rajesh.singh@example.com",
  "gender": "Male",
  "dob": "1995-08-15",
  "address": "H.No 124, Sector 15",
  "city": "Gurugram",
  "state": "Haryana",
  "pincode": "122001",
  "profilePicture": "https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg"
}

###

### 6. Create Booking (नई सर्विस बुक करें)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/bookings/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "categoryId": "cat_plumber",
  "subServiceId": "sub_pl_leak",
  "dateTime": "2026-07-20T10:00:00Z",
  "timeSlot": "10:00 AM - 12:00 PM",
  "address": "H.No 124, Sector 15, Gurugram",
  "problemDescription": "Bathroom kitchen tap is leaking constantly",
  "hasVoiceNote": false,
  "paymentMethod": "UPI"
}

###

### 7. Get User Bookings List (बुकिंग हिस्ट्री देखें)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/bookings/user
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### 8. Get Notifications (नोटिफिकेशन देखें)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### 9. Register Device FCM Token (FCM टोकन दर्ज करें)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/device-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "fcmToken": "fcm_token_demo_1234567890",
  "deviceId": "device_id_windows_11"
}

###

### 10. Validate Coupon Code (कूपन कोड चेक करें)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/coupons/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "couponCode": "SGSAVE30",
  "basePrice": 399
}

###

### 11. Add Saved Address (एड्रेस सेव करें)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/user/addresses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "addressLine": "Flat 302, Phase 3, Green Gardens",
  "city": "Noida",
  "state": "Uttar Pradesh",
  "pincode": "201301",
  "isDefault": true
}

###

### 12. Get Saved Addresses List (सेव किए पते देखें)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/user/addresses
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

###

### 13. Upload Work Photos (काम के पहले/बाद के फोटो अपलोड करें - एक्सपर्ट)
# नोट: :id को वास्तविक बुकिंग आईडी (जैसे: bk_1784329314847) से बदलें
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/bookings/:id/photos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "type": "before",
  "photos": [
    "https://example.com/work_before_1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/work_before_2.jpg"
  ]
}

